@DATABASE MUINames
@NODE Main "MUINames"

MUINames
========

A plug-in for @{"MUIVideo" LINK //Dokumentation/MUIVideo.guide/MAIN} as a database for lists
of names (directors, composers, actors and authors).


@{" Introduction    " LINK Intro}  What is MUINames ?
