@ENDNODE
@NODE Intro "Intrduction"

What is MUINames ?
------------------

MUINames is a plug-in for MUIVideo. @{"MUIVideo" LINK //Dokumentation/MUIVideo.guide/MAIN} is a videofilm-database.

MUINames is an additon for MUIVideo, a database for lists of names.
In this version directors, authors, composers and actors are supported.

Data exchange between the two programs is done via the ARexx-port of them.

@ENDNODE
